01:02:12.480 --> 01:02:16.360
but what is the level
of quality that's needed

01:02:16.360 --> 01:02:18.050
for that non-infringing use.

01:02:18.050 --> 01:02:20.670
I'm not always convinced that
it's something we can measure.

01:02:20.670 --> 01:02:22.460
It's something we can argue for.

01:02:22.460 --> 01:02:25.260
But I don't know that
it's ever measurable,

01:02:25.260 --> 01:02:28.010
except with a lot of anecdotes.

